                     <p>Abbreviated sewing at two stations, possibly on supports, with Islamic-style twined chevron endbands in green and red <material>silk</material> threads at head and tail. 
                        Covered in full, tight-backed polished red goatskin <material>leather</material> over <material>pasteboards</material>.</p>
